Package org.lindbergframework.beans.di

Interface Summary
BeanMapper Interface that defines the contract for Bean Mappers inside of IOC context.
DependencyManager Interface that defines the contract for a Dependency Manager inside of IOC context.
 

Class Summary
AnnotationClassPathBeanMapper Bean mapper implementation for annotated classes with Bean annotation inside application class path.
AnnotationDependencyManager DependencyManager Implementation for to manage dependecies by annotation Inject.
BeanMapping Class that defines bean mapping inside of IOC context.
